*Context and Operators (Page 6 of 6)*

=== Context Atoms ===
`#!` - current channel
`@!` - current user

=== Data Types ===
Numbers, strings, lists, booleans (`true`/`false`), and `nil`.

=== Operators ===
Arithmetic: `+ - * / mod`
Comparison: `= == != > < >= <=`
Logic: `and or not && ||`

=== Lists ===
Literal: `[1, 2, 3]`
Index: `list[0]` or `(index list 0)`

